Kia Ora!
Welcome to I Book a Ride. We are a private travel company that can book vehicles in Auckland, and in a few North Island regions.
We provide travel at affordable rates for personal, and professional requirements.
With our user-friendly system, you can select rides, and options for you, by you.
You will be the one selecting everything and entering all the details in a click. 
There's a maximum of 250 passengers on your booking., as we aim to provide a premium experience whilst you travel.

Here are our prices:

